description: Dept. of Elections - Elected Mr. Gurusinghedapanadurage Amal Nishantha Samarasinghe as a member of the Madurawala Pradeshiya Sabha - Vacating the office of member of Nuwara Eliya Pradeshiya Sabha by Mr. Ramiah Malarvasagam and Mr. Kadiravel Kalyanakumara - Elected Mr. Wimalasiri Jayalath as a member of the Kuruwita Pradeshya Sabha
